{"_id":"socialite","name":"Socialite","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":-2,"grace":2,"speed":-1,"resilience":-1,"charm":3,"cunning":1,"intellect":2,"tenacity":-1},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"3 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"art":{"value":2},"barter":{"value":1},"bewitch":{"value":3},"convince":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":1},"gambling":{"value":1},"literacy":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":1},"bureaucracy":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Governor's Gift","description":"Choose a gender. Gain + on Bewitch and Scrutiny duels vs chosen gender."},{"name":"Grace Under Fire","description":"Uses Grace instead of Speed for Defense and Initiative."},{"name":"Don't Mind Me (11)","description":"If no offensive actions last turn, enemies must succeed TN 11 Scrutiny Challenge or choose different target."}],"actions":["(1) B&D Pocket (Pistol) | AV: 2 (7) | Rg: z6 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/3 damage. Capacity 4, Reload 2."],"notes":"Highest echelons of Malifaux society. Weaponize gossip, bribery, and conspiracy to ruin rivals for sport."}}
{"_id":"convict-gunslinger","name":"Convict Gunslinger","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (11)","willpower":"4 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":3},"carouse":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":2},"gambling":{"value":1},"intimidation":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":4},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Return Fire (Mask)","description":"After this character succeeds, attacker suffers damage from one of this character's readied Pistol weapons. Damage flip receives -."},{"name":"Bulletproof +1","description":"Reduce all damage from Ranged Combat attacks by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Gunfighter","description":"May use Pistols as if Range y2."},{"name":"Relentless","description":"Immune to Horror Duels."}],"actions":["(1) Weshorn & Smitte (Pistol) | AV: 5 (12) | Rg: y2 or z10 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 1. Ram Critical Strike: +1 per Ram."],"notes":"Condemned criminals pressed into Soulstone mine labor who escaped. Survive as hired guns, always moving, always watching."}}
{"_id":"desperate-mercenary","name":"Desperate Mercenary","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":1,"resilience":-1,"charm":0,"cunning":1,"intellect":1,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"3 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":5},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":1},"barter":{"value":2},"convince":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":2},"labor":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Combat Reading","description":"When making disengaging strikes, add Scrutiny (+2) to Acting Value."},{"name":"Reckless","description":"At start of turn, may suffer 1 damage to gain 1 additional General AP."}],"actions":["(1) Brahk'blade (Labor) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. No Triggers.","(1) Collier Navy (Pistol) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 2. Ram Unload: If 2+ bullets remain, +2 damage and weapon empty."],"notes":"Failed immigrants taking jobs no reputable mercenary will touch — extortion, kidnapping, murder. Survive at any cost."}}
{"_id":"ronin","name":"Ronin","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":1,"resilience":1,"charm":1,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"3 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"literacy":{"value":1},"labor":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":2},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":2},"track":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Disguised","description":"Cannot be targeted by Charge Action."},{"name":"Hard to Kill","description":"May choose to ignore one Critical Effect per Dramatic Time."},{"name":"Take the Hit","description":"After attack hits nearby ally, may discard card to move between ally and attacker, suffering effect instead (-to damage flip). Opponents engaged cannot make Disengaging Strikes."}],"actions":["(1) Daito (Labor) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage, ignoring Armor. Mask Next Target: Move up to 4 yards after damaging. Crow Twist: +.","(1) Collier Navy (Pistol) | AV: 4 (10) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 2.","(2) Flurry | Discard Twist to take three (1) AP attacks with Close Combat weapon vs single target."],"notes":"Masterless wanderers, escaped convicts or fugitives. Hire as cheap bodyguards. Travel in disguise, always moving."}}
{"_id":"bandit","name":"Bandit","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-2,"cunning":0,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"5 (10)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":3},"centering":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidation":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Quick Getaway (Mask)","description":"After resolving vs enemy, push this character up to 5 yards in any direction."},{"name":"Bulletproof +1","description":"Reduce all Ranged Combat damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Gunfighter","description":"May use Pistols as if Range y2."}],"actions":["(1) Collier Navy (Pistol) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y2 or z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 2. Tome Drop It: Target passes TN 10 Centering duel or drops held item.","(2) Run and Gun | Discard Twist. Move up to Walk, make (1) AP Ranged Combat attack, move up to Walk."],"notes":"Many escaped convicts plaguing the Northern Hills and Contract Towns. Rob mining towns and Guild trains."}}
{"_id":"rogue-construct","name":"Rogue Construct","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Construct","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":-2,"speed":-1,"resilience":4,"charm":-2,"cunning":1,"intellect":3,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"3 (10)","willpower":"4 (11)","walk":"4","charge":"6","height":"3","initiative":"-1 (6)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"artefacting":{"value":2},"athletics":{"value":3},"convince":{"value":1},"deceive":{"value":3},"engineering":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"heavyGuns":{"value":2},"intimidation":{"value":2},"mathematics":{"value":3},"labor":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +2","description":"Reduce all damage by 2 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Constant Upgrades","description":"After 5 min salvaging destroyed Construct, discard card to gain ability, Skill, Attribute, or weapon. Cannot raise Armor above +3."},{"name":"No Masters","description":"May never be subordinate character."},{"name":"Rush +2","description":"Charge Aspect increased by +2."}],"actions":["(1) Enlarged Spiked Club (Labor) | AV: 5 (12) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 3/4/5 damage. Destroys Brittle items. Ram Shatter: Push target 2 yards and it becomes Prone."],"notes":"Guild/M&SU constructs kept operational by Soulstones risk soul contamination. Fragments coalesce into composite sentience—Rogue Construct."}}
{"_id":"freikorpsmann","name":"Freikorpsmann","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Freikorps","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-1,"cunning":0,"intellect":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":1},"bewitch":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidation":{"value":2},"labor":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Freikorps Suit","description":"Ignores all damage from pulse and blast effects."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Hunting Knife (Labor) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage. Ram Critical Strike: +1 per Ram. Tome Duck & Weave: +2 Defense until start of next turn.","(1) Clockwork Pistol (Pistol) | AV: 6 (12) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/4/5 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 2. Ram Critical Strike: +1 per Ram. Mask Reposition: Move up to 3 yards.","(0) Freikorps Tactics | Discard card to add suit of choice to every duel until start of next turn."],"notes":"Rank-and-file Freikorps trained and tested as cohesive units. Know fallen ally will be cared for by Von Schill."}}
{"_id":"freikorps-trapper","name":"Freikorps Trapper","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Freikorps","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-1,"cunning":0,"intellect":2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidation":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"labor":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":1},"track":{"value":3},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Freikorps Suit","description":"Ignores all damage from pulse and blast effects."},{"name":"From the Shadows","description":"If no enemy aware of this character, may immediately take one additional turn after Initiative flip before characters resolve turns."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Hunting Knife (Labor) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage.","(1) Clockwork Rifle (Long Arms) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage. Gains + to attack flip. Range +10 per + from Focused. Capacity 1, Reload 2. Ram Critical Strike: +1 per Ram.","(0) Freikorps Tactics | Discard card to add suit of choice to every duel until start of next turn."],"notes":"Scout-snipers selected for tracking and hunting expertise. Earn additional revenue through pelts and furs."}}
{"_id":"void-wretch","name":"Void Wretch","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Void","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":3,"speed":1,"resilience":0,"charm":-5,"cunning":-2,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"7 (13)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"1","initiative":"3 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":5},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":5},"necromancy":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"prestidigitation":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1},"track":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters and terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half (rounded up)."},{"name":"Pure Nothingness","description":"At end of each Dramatic Time round, suffer cumulative -1 Df (minimum 0)."},{"name":"Time is Meaningless","description":"Gain ++ on all duels vs characters with Fast Condition."}],"actions":["(1) Touch of the Void (Necromancy) | AV: 4 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Wp | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage and becomes Slow.","(1) Phase Through (Athletics) | TN: 10 | Target moves up to 8 yards through terrain and other characters."],"notes":"Sentient nothingness given purpose by Tyrant Obliteration. Exist between dimensions. Only survive few hours before reality fills them in."}}
{"_id":"freikorps-librarian","name":"Freikorps Librarian","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living, Freikorps","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":1,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-1,"cunning":2,"intellect":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (11)","willpower":"6 (13)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":1},"bewitch":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":4},"counterSpelling":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidation":{"value":2},"leadership":{"value":2},"literacy":{"value":3},"labor":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"sorcery":{"value":4},"toughness":{"value":2},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Freikorps Suit","description":"Ignores all damage from pulse and blast effects."},{"name":"Litany of Healing","description":"Friendly characters within a6 gain Regeneration +1. Freikorps characters gain Regeneration +2."},{"name":"Nether Fluctuations","description":"Enemy characters within a6 ignore suit associations from their Skills."}],"actions":["(1) Hunting Knife (Labor) | AV: 4 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage.","(1) Ancient Words (Sorcery) | AV: 6T (13T) | TN: 13T | Rg: 10 | Resist: Wp | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage, ignoring Armor and Hard to Wound. Mask Words of Binding: Target becomes Slow. Tome Resonance: +B to Moderate and Severe damage.","(2) Furious Casting | Discard Twist to take three (1) AP attack actions with Spell vs single target."],"notes":"Magical support specialists. Intelligence analysts and chant ancient words from recovered Grimoires. Knowledge is the warriors sharpest weapon."}}
{"_id":"freikorps-drache-trooper","name":"Freikorps Drache Trooper","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living, Freikorps","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":1,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"3 (10)","willpower":"5 (12)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":1},"bewitch":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"heavyGuns":{"value":4},"intimidation":{"value":3},"leadership":{"value":2},"labor":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":3},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +2","description":"Reduce all damage by 2 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Assault Training","description":"May treat Flamethrowers as if Range y3."},{"name":"Freikorps Suit","description":"Ignores all damage from pulse and blast effects."},{"name":"Punctured Tanks","description":"If suffering Critical Effect targeting Chest (Ram), discard card to avoid it. If not, killed and characters within p3 suffer 1 damage and Burning +2."}],"actions":["(1) Flamethrower (Heavy Guns) | AV: 6R (13R) | Rg: y3 or z10 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3B/4BB damage and Burning +1. Grants + to Intimidate. Ram Youre Flammable: +1 Burning per Ram. Crow Sadistic Laughter: TN 10 Horror Duel. Capacity 20, Reload 8.","(1) Move or Burn | Friendly characters within p10 with Slow or Paralyzed lose it and gain Burning +1.","(0) Freikorps Tactics | Discard card to add suit of choice to every duel until start of next turn."],"notes":"Elite Freikorps trained with Wyrms Breath flamethrowers. Encased in armored suits with chemical canisters. Terrifying on battlefield."}}
{"_id":"void-hunter","name":"Void Hunter","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Void","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":3,"speed":3,"resilience":2,"charm":-5,"cunning":2,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"7 (15)","willpower":"5 (13)","walk":"6","charge":"7","height":"2","initiative":"5 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":3},"counterSpelling":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":5},"necromancy":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"prestidigitation":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":3},"track":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Borrowed Time (Tome)","description":"After failing, summon Void Wretch within 1 yard. Attacker must discard card or become Fast until next turn."},{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters and terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half."},{"name":"Pure Nothingness","description":"At end of each Dramatic Time round, suffer cumulative -1 Df (minimum 0)."},{"name":"Terrifying (Living) (12)","description":"Enemy Living characters must pass TN 12 Horror Duel when ending turn within engagement range or targeting this character."},{"name":"Time is Meaningless","description":"Gain ++ on all duels vs characters with Fast Condition."}],"actions":["(1) Obliterate (Necromancy) | AV: 6 (14) | Rg: y3 | Resist: Wp | Target suffers 2/5/6 damage. Tome Glimpse the Void: Target must pass TN 13 Willpower duel or be removed from reality until end of round. Ram Evaporate: Target suffers Severe Critical Effect.","(0) Deja Vu (Prestidigitation) | AV: 6 (14) | Rg: 10 | Resist: Wp | Target becomes Slow. If was Fast, this character heals 2 damage and may teleport within 1 yard of target."],"notes":"Patient stalking predators. Ambush through solid surfaces. Each bite causes flesh to evaporate. Shedding fragments become new Void Wretches."}}
{"_id":"abomination","name":"Abomination","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct, Undead, Horror","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":1,"speed":2,"resilience":-1,"charm":-5,"cunning":-3,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"3 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":1},"pugilism":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Caustic Aura","description":"Living characters beginning turn within a2 suffer 1 damage and cannot declare (0) Actions until next turn."},{"name":"Controlled Deformation","description":"If within 2 yards of 3+ characters with this ability at start of turn, absorbs them and becomes Desolation Engine. New Engine cannot act this round."},{"name":"Horrifying Presence","description":"When this character is created or revealed to Living characters, each must pass TN 10 Horror Duel."}],"actions":["(1) Grasping Limbs (Pugilism) | AV: 3 (8) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage and becomes Slow.","(0) Absorb Corpse | If within 2 yards of a dead Living character, absorb it and heal 1 damage."],"notes":"Horrifying amalgamations of mechanical devices and rotting flesh from Old Malifaux. Warp living flesh when near. Can absorb bodies to repair themselves."}}
{"_id":"guild-huntmaster","name":"Guild Huntmaster","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Guardsman","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":1,"cunning":-1,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"2 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":1},"flexible":{"value":2},"husbandry":{"value":2},"leadership":{"value":1},"pistol":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1},"track":{"value":1},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Down, Boy!","description":"Does not flip for friendly Hound characters when determining random target when entering engagement range."},{"name":"My Dogs Are Hungry!","description":"Friendly Hounds within a6 may declare the (2) Charge Action as a (1) Action."}],"actions":["(1) Barbed Whip (Flexible) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage. Crow Motivation: After succeeding, move target 1 yard if this attack dealt Weak damage, 2 yards if Moderate or Severe.","(1) Collier Navy (Pistol) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Capacity 6, Reload 2."],"notes":"Guild's first Huntmasters. Control packs of trained Hounds. Coordinate with Guard Dogs."}}
{"_id":"desolation-engine","name":"Desolation Engine","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Construct, Undead","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":-2,"speed":1,"resilience":5,"charm":-5,"cunning":-3,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"3 (11)","willpower":"5 (13)","walk":"5","charge":"8","height":"3","initiative":"3 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":12},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":3},"necromancy":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":5}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hard to Wound +2","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer --."},{"name":"Caustic Aura","description":"Living characters beginning turn within a2 suffer 2 damage and cannot declare (0) Actions until next turn."},{"name":"Desolate Warping","description":"After killing Living, Construct, or Undead, may discard card to transform it into Abomination that cannot act this round. This character heals to full Wounds."},{"name":"Lost Focus","description":"If killed, becomes two Abominations that cannot act this round."},{"name":"Melee Expert","description":"Generates 1 additional AP on turn, but only for Close Combat attacks."},{"name":"Rush +3","description":"Charge Aspect increased by +3."}],"actions":["(1) Entropy Claws (Pugilism) | AV: 6T (14T) | Rg: y3 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 3/4/6 damage. Tome Consuming Touch: After damaging, heals amount equal to damage target suffered.","(1) Desolate Supplications (Necromancy) | This character may suffer up to 4 damage. Every character within p6 must pass TN 13 Toughness duel or suffer damage equal to what this character suffered -1."],"notes":"Towering monstrosities formed when 4+ Abominations converge. Ooze putrid fluid from seams. Heal by consuming. No loyalty - attack anyone. Only annihilation ends the cycle."}}
{"_id":"rotten-belle","name":"Rotten Belle","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Undead, Belle","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":2,"cunning":1,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"bewitch":{"value":3},"deceive":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hard to Wound +1","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer -."},{"name":"Pounce","description":"When enemy ends push or move within engagement range not part of Walk or Charge, may immediately take (1) AP Close Combat attack."}],"actions":["(1) Teeth and Nails (Pugilism) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage.","(1) Lure (Bewitch) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: 18 | Resist: Wp | Living target moves yards equal to its Walk toward this character. Mask Confusing Feelings: Target gains Confusing Feelings Condition until end of next turn (suffers - on all defense duels).","(1) Undress (Bewitch) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: 6 | Resist: Wp | Living target becomes Slow."],"notes":"Disturbingly attractive in moldering dresses. Lurk near old haunts. Hide decaying faces until prey close. Fresher Belles can giggle and sway invitingly."}}
{"_id":"dead-doxy","name":"Dead Doxy","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Undead, Belle","aspects":{"might":-2,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":3,"charm":3,"cunning":2,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":2},"bewitch":{"value":3},"deceive":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":3},"melee":{"value":3},"music":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Flick of the Wrist","description":"May use Grace instead of Might for Melee or Pugilism attacks."},{"name":"Hard to Wound +1","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer -."},{"name":"Inviting Allure","description":"When character within a6 becomes Slow, may discard card to force it to move yards equal to its Walk toward this character."},{"name":"Manipulative (10)","description":"When enemy targets this character, they must pass TN 10 Willpower Challenge. On failure, may change target to legal target of choice."}],"actions":["(1) Fancy Cane (Melee) | AV: 6 (12) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/2/4 damage. Severe damage inflicts Weak Critical Effect. Ram Out Clubbing: After damaging, target knocked Prone, take action again vs same target.","(1) Undress (Bewitch) | AV: 6T (12T) | Rg: 6 | Resist: Wp | Living target becomes Slow. Tome Burlesque Show: Living characters within p3 must make TN 13 Centering Challenge or become Slow. Mask Confusing Feelings: After succeeding, target gains Confusing Feelings until end of next turn."],"notes":"Undead performers reanimated by necromancers. Retain grace and showmanship. Walk with confident strides not shambling. Seductive manner can freeze attackers."}}
{"_id":"crooligan","name":"Crooligan","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Undead, Horror, Lost","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":4,"speed":2,"resilience":0,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"6 (11)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"1","initiative":"4 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":1},"enchanting":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":4},"lockpicking":{"value":1},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pickPocket":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":4}},"abilities":[{"name":"From the Shadows","description":"When called on Initiative flip, if no enemy aware is unfriendly, may immediately take one additional turn after flip (before characters resolve) for each instance. If multiple characters have this, resolve in Initiative order."}],"actions":["(1) Infected Dagger (Melee) | AV: 3C (8C) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage. Crow Infect: After succeeding, target gains Poison +1 Condition number of times equal to Crow in final duel total.","(1) Return to Sender | Teleport to space within 1 yard of controller regardless of distance, or within 1 yard of any character within 12 yards fully in soft cover.","(1) The Mist (Enchanting) | AV: 5C (10C) | TN: 10C | Until start of next turn (or controller's next turn if subordinate), area within a4 considered Ht 3 soft cover."],"notes":"Abused children changed by mist. Ragged silhouettes with dead eyes. Abusers who follow victims into fog find themselves confronted - by morning, no trace remains."}}
{"_id":"zombie-swordsman","name":"Zombie Swordsman","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Undead, Horror","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":1,"resilience":3,"charm":-5,"cunning":-1,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"2 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hard to Kill","description":"May choose to ignore one Critical Effect per Dramatic Time."},{"name":"Hard to Wound +1","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer -."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores penalties for terrain while taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Paired Swords (Melee) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Action gains + to attack flip.","(1) Slice and Dice (Melee) | All characters within p3 must succeed TN 11 Defense duel or suffer damage flip with one wielded sword. Damage flip receives -.","(2) Flurry | Discard Twist to take three (1) AP attacks with Close Combat weapon vs single target."],"notes":"Retain muscle memory from life. Reanimated corpses of skilled swordsmen are prized by Resurrectionists. Fearless and immune to pain."}}
{"_id":"resurrectionist","name":"Resurrectionist","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Living, Tormented","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":-2,"speed":1,"resilience":2,"charm":2,"cunning":2,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":1},"derived":{"defense":"3 (11)","willpower":"5 (13)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"3 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"centering":{"value":3},"deceive":{"value":2},"doctor":{"value":1},"intimidate":{"value":2},"leadership":{"value":1},"literacy":{"value":1},"necromancy":{"value":4},"notice":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":3},"stitching":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Restless Dead","description":"Mindless Zombies are immune to Slow and gain +4 Pugilism while within a6."},{"name":"Zombie Apocalypse","description":"Accompanied by and controls number of Mindless Zombies equal to Rank Value."}],"actions":["(1) Drain Life (Necromancy) | AV: 5C (13C) | TN: 12C | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Living target suffers 1/3/4 damage, then heals equal to damage inflicted. Crow Fleeting Breath: After killing Living target, reanimates as Mindless Zombie.","(1) Rigor Mortis (Necromancy) | AV: 5C (13C) | TN: 10C | Rg: 10 | Resist: Wp | Living target becomes Slow. Undead becomes Fast. Mask Zombie Food: Friendly Mindless Zombies may take (1) AP Close Combat attack.","(0) Raise Undead | Discard card to animate corpse within 5 yards as Mindless Zombie under control."],"notes":"Practicing necromancer who commands undead minions. Commands zombies equal to Rank Value. Field commanders for undead forces."}}
{"_id":"shieldbearer","name":"Shieldbearer","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":3,"grace":-2,"speed":1,"resilience":0,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"3 (8)","willpower":"6 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"2 (7)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":1},"centering":{"value":4},"evade":{"value":2},"heavyMelee":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":3},"necromancy":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Dismember","description":"When attack causes Severe Critical Effect, may discard card to change Critical Effect to Amputated without changing location."},{"name":"Tethered Soul","description":"If killed within 6 yards of friendly Enforcer/Henchman/Master, that character may discard card to bind spirit, transforming into friendly Shackled Spirit appearing adjacent to corpse (cannot act this round)."}],"actions":["(1) Salvaged Greatsword (Heavy Melee) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 3/4/6 damage. Damage flip gains + if not from Charge Action.","(1) Shield Slam (Melee) | AV: 6 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage and pushed 1 yard away."],"notes":"Desperate slum-dwellers inspired by Reva Cortinas. Took up salvaged Guardian weapons and shields. Rise as Shackled Spirits when fallen."}}
{"_id":"nurse","name":"Nurse","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Tormented","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":2,"cunning":1,"intellect":2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"6 (12)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"3 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"doctor":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":4},"literacy":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":1},"prestidigitation":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hands Off (Mask)","description":"After damaged by y attack, may immediately move yards equal to Walk in any direction."},{"name":"Flick of the Wrist","description":"Use Grace instead of Might for Melee and Pugilism attacks."},{"name":"Illegible Prescriptions","description":"During duel, may end Focused Condition to add any suit to final duel total."}],"actions":["(1) Surgical Instruments (Melee) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage, ignoring Hard to Wound.","(1) Syringe (Melee) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 0/0/1 damage and gains Poison +4. Ram Overdose: Target suffers 2/3/4 and no Poison.","(1) Take Your Meds (Doctor) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: 8 | Resist: Wp | Target gains Condition until start of next turn: Ram Hallucinogens, Mask Uppers, Tome Downers, or Crow Painkillers."],"notes":"McMourning promised nurses eternal youth through skin transplant. Psychological trauma drives insanity. Experts in anesthetics. Serve in Guild morgue and Quarantine Zone lab."}}
{"_id":"shackled-spirit","name":"Shackled Spirit","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Spirit, Retainer","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":-1,"speed":3,"resilience":0,"charm":-4,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"5 (10)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"6","charge":"7","height":"2","initiative":"4 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"centering":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":2},"martialArts":{"value":2},"necromancy":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Shackled Servitude","description":"Within 6 yards of friendly Enforcer/Henchman/Master, gains + to attack flips."},{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters/terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half."}],"actions":["(1) Spectral Claws (Martial Arts) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage. Crow Chill of Death: Target gains Chill of Death Condition until start of next turn (suffers - on Physical Aspect duels).","(0) Soulfire (Necromancy) | AV: 5C (10C) | Rg: 8 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage, then character fades away and is killed."],"notes":"Spirits bound to mortal realm by necromantic ritual. Denied passage to afterlife. Furious and enslaved. Rise from fallen Shieldbearers."}}
{"_id":"simulacrum","name":"Simulacrum","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Undead, Horror","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":-3,"speed":-2,"resilience":4,"charm":-5,"cunning":-3,"intellect":-4,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"2 (10)","willpower":"5 (13)","walk":"3","charge":"6","height":"3","initiative":"-2 (6)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":11},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":5},"pugilism":{"value":2},"thrownWeapons":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":5}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hard to Wound +2","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer --."},{"name":"Rush +3","description":"Charge Aspect increased by +3."},{"name":"Terrifying (Living) (12)","description":"Enemy Living characters must pass TN 12 Horror Duel when ending turn in engagement range or targeting."},{"name":"Walking Morgue","description":"If limbs severed/destroyed, reanimates as two Mindless Zombies (cannot act). If killed, becomes six Mindless Zombies (cannot act)."}],"actions":["(1) Meaty Fists (Pugilism) | AV: 6 (14) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 3/5/6 damage. Mask Knockabout: Push target up to 5 yards. Crow Loose Pieces: Summon Mindless Zombie in base contact (cannot act), suffer 1 damage.","(1) Hurl Zombie (Thrown Weapons) | AV: 6 (14) | Rg: z10 | Resist: Df | Throw friendly Mindless Zombie at target. Target suffers 2/4/5 damage and Prone. Zombie suffers 2 damage, placed within 1 yard, becomes Prone."],"notes":"Massive brutes stitched from dozens of corpses. Graveyard's worth per creation. Severing limb releases Mindless Zombies. Inspire revulsion."}}
{"_id":"mindless-zombie","name":"Mindless Zombie","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Peon","value":4},"types":"Undead","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":-3,"speed":-3,"resilience":0,"charm":-5,"cunning":-5,"intellect":-5,"tenacity":-5},"derived":{"defense":"2 (6)","willpower":"2 (6)","walk":"3","charge":"3","height":"2","initiative":"-3 (1)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"pugilism":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Hard to Wound +1","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer -."},{"name":"Shambling","description":"Gains Slow at start of each turn during Dramatic Time."},{"name":"Zombie Curse","description":"Any Living character killed by this character animates as Mindless Zombie one hour after death."}],"actions":["(1) Gnashing Bite (Pugilism) | AV: 3 (7) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/3 damage. Increase AV by +1 for every other friendly character engaged with target."],"notes":"Weakest of all undead. Incapable of higher thought. Dangerous only in numbers but grow quickly. Death Marshals respond to every report seriously."}}
{"_id":"sorrow","name":"Sorrow","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Spirit, Woe","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":-1,"resilience":0,"charm":-4,"cunning":0,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"3 (8)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"-1 (4)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"evade":{"value":1},"intimidate":{"value":2},"prestidigitation":{"value":3},"pugilism":{"value":2},"stealth":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Dont Mind Me (10)","description":"If did not take offensive actions last turn, or first round and not acted, enemies targeting must succeed TN 10 Scrutiny or choose different target."},{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters/terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half."},{"name":"Life Leech","description":"Enemy characters beginning turn within a1 suffer 1 damage; character heals 1 damage."},{"name":"Misery","description":"When enemy within 6 yards fails Willpower duel, suffers 1 damage after resolving."}],"actions":["(1) Doleful Grasp (Pugilism) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage. Mask Melancholy: Target gains Nobody Likes Me Condition until sunrise/sunset (- on Social duels, acts last in Dramatic Time).","(1) Doldrums (Prestidigitation) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: 6 | Resist: Wp | Target becomes Slow. If already Slow, becomes Paralyzed."],"notes":"Physical manifestations of despondency. Attract and are attracted by depression. Sap spirit of opponents. Victims see little reason to resist. Feed on despair."}}
{"_id":"poltergeist","name":"Poltergeist","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Woe, Spirit","aspects":{"might":-2,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-2,"cunning":1,"intellect":2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"6 (12)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"3","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"centering":{"value":4},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"prestidigitation":{"value":2},"thrownWeapons":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Distracting Whispers","description":"Enemy characters within a2 suffer - to Willpower duels."},{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters/terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half."},{"name":"Misery","description":"When enemy within 6 yards fails Willpower duel, suffers 1 damage after resolving."},{"name":"Regeneration +1","description":"Heals 1 damage at start of turn during Dramatic Time."}],"actions":["(1) Hurl Heavy Object (Thrown Weapons) | AV: 6 (12) | Rg: z9 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Ram Crushing Strike: Damage flip gains + per Ram. Mask Forceful Push: After succeeding, push up to 3 yards and Prone.","(1) Paranormal Activity (Prestidigitation) | Every character within p6 must succeed TN 12 Willpower duel or become Slow. Character may move unattended objects 200 lbs or less within 6 yards to other location within 6 yards. Once per turn only."],"notes":"Much more active than Sorrows. Little patience for slow mental collapse. Telekinetic rage. Haunt buildings - homes, libraries, warehouses. Powerful Neverborn bind them as servants."}}
{"_id":"terror-tot","name":"Terror Tot","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living, Nephilim","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":3,"speed":4,"resilience":0,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"6 (11)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"6","charge":"8","height":"1","initiative":"5 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":2},"martialArts":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":2},"track":{"value":1},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Black Blood","description":"All characters without Black Blood within 1 yard suffer 1 damage when this character suffers damage."},{"name":"Pounce","description":"When enemy ends push or move within engagement range not part of Walk/Charge, may immediately take (1) AP Close Combat attack."},{"name":"Grow","description":"If kills Living non-Nephilim with y attack, may feast on remains to become Young Nephilim. All damage and Conditions removed."}],"actions":["(1) Blackened Claws (Martial Arts) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage.","(0) Sprint (Athletics) | Character may discard card to take Walk Action."],"notes":"Youngest Nephilim. Small size belies ruthlessness. Cannot yet fly. Use hooves to spring at enemies. Hunt in packs. Feed on corpses to grow into Young Nephilim."}}
{"_id":"young-nephilim","name":"Young Nephilim","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Nephilim","aspects":{"might":3,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":-3,"cunning":2,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"athletics":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":2},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Black Blood","description":"All characters without Black Blood within 1 yard suffer 1 damage when this character suffers damage."},{"name":"Flight","description":"Immune to falling damage. May ignore terrain and other characters when moving."},{"name":"Thirst for Blood","description":"Gains Fast Condition when Living character within 3 yards killed by friendly character."},{"name":"Mature","description":"If kills Living non-Nephilim Enforcer/Henchman/Master rank or Fated with y attack, may feast to become Mature Nephilim. All damage/Conditions removed."}],"actions":["(1) Talons (Pugilism) | AV: 6M (12M) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/4/5 damage. Ram Blood Frenzy: After damaging, take action again vs same target. Mask Toss Away: Push target 4 yards. Mask Feed Brood: Push corpse 4 yards, Terror Tots count as killing for Grow."],"notes":"Grown from Terror Tots after consuming blood. Sudden violent growth process. Ravenous appetite. Hunt in packs of 2-3. Trigger growth through feasting."}}
{"_id":"mature-nephilim","name":"Mature Nephilim","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Living, Nephilim","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":3,"speed":3,"resilience":4,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (12)","willpower":"5 (13)","walk":"6","charge":"7","height":"3","initiative":"5 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":10},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"melee":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":4},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by 1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Black Blood","description":"All characters without Black Blood within 1 yard suffer 1 damage when this character suffers damage."},{"name":"Flight","description":"Immune to falling damage. May ignore terrain and other characters when moving."},{"name":"Terrifying (Living) (12)","description":"Enemy Living must pass TN 12 Horror Duel when ending turn in engagement range or targeting."}],"actions":["(1) Monstrous Talons (Pugilism) | AV: 7M (15M) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 4/5/6 damage. Mask/Tome Charge Through: Instead of damage, push target 4 yards. Mask/Crow Rip in Half: After killing, all enemies within p6 make TN 12 Horror Duel."],"notes":"Hulking creatures twice human height. Strong claws tear men apart. Keenly intelligent. Swift and strong. Even other Nephilim fear them. Never stop growing. Blood drinking fuels further growth."}}
{"_id":"insidious-madness","name":"Insidious Madness","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Nightmare, Woe","aspects":{"might":-4,"grace":-2,"speed":2,"resilience":-2,"charm":-2,"cunning":1,"intellect":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"7","charge":"—","height":"2","initiative":"3 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"notice":{"value":1},"prestidigitation":{"value":2},"thrownWeapons":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Better Part of Valor","description":"Walk increased by +2 but has no Charge Aspect."},{"name":"Incorporeal","description":"Ignores other characters/terrain during movement. Reduce Ranged/Close Combat damage by half."},{"name":"Insidious Whispers","description":"Character ending turn within a3 must pass TN 8 Centering or gain Crazy +1 (- to Mental Aspect duels, may hear voices)."}],"actions":["(1) Touch of Madness (Prestidigitation) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Wp | Target suffers damage equal to Repressed Memories value, then gains Repressed Memories +1 until end of day (Initiative reduced). Crow Deepest Fears: Target must discard card.","(1) Psychotic Influence (Prestidigitation) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: 9 | Resist: Wp | Target suffers 1/2/2 damage and gains Crazy +1. Crow Induce Phobia: After damaging, target makes TN 10 Horror Duel."],"notes":"Physical manifestations of madness pooled in sunken places. Ever-changing horrific form. Float languidly toward victims. Twisted whispers form demented thoughts and visions."}}
{"_id":"doppleganger","name":"Doppleganger","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living, Woe, Mimic","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":3,"resilience":1,"charm":2,"cunning":3,"intellect":1,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (12)","willpower":"5 (12)","walk":"6","charge":"7","height":"2","initiative":"6 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"carouse":{"value":1},"convince":{"value":4},"deceive":{"value":5},"enchanting":{"value":4},"forgery":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":2},"leadership":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"pickPocket":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Manipulative (11)","description":"When enemy targets with Action, must pass TN 11 Willpower Challenge. On failure, may change target to legal target."},{"name":"Which One Is Real?","description":"When randomizing targets in melee, may discard card to have attack target character of choice."}],"actions":["(1) Sharp Knife (Melee) | AV: 4 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage. If target engaged with enemy, attack deals +2 damage. Ram Vital Strike: +2 damage and target Slow.","(0) Mimic (Enchanting) | Character changes appearance (clothing but not weapons) to match humanoid within 8 yards. Perfect duplication including voice, scars, birthmarks. Pneumatic limbs appear but not actual. Lasts until used again."],"notes":"Shapeshanger that wears human faces from murdered victims. Change form with thought. Flesh shifts until settling on desired form. Patient and crafty. Wait weeks/months/years impersonating victims."}}
{"_id":"waldgeist","name":"Waldgeist","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living, Swampfiend, Beast","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":3,"charm":-2,"cunning":3,"intellect":0,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"5 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"enchanting":{"value":4},"evade":{"value":4},"notice":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":1},"track":{"value":3},"wilderness":{"value":4}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +2","description":"Reduce all damage by +2 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Walking Tree","description":"Indistinguishable from normal tree when not moving."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Tangling Roots (Enchanting) | AV: 7M (12M) | Rg: y2 or y4 in severe terrain | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage. Mask Entangle: After damaging, target Slow. Mask/Tome Entrench: Target gains Rooted Condition until end of next turn (no Walk/Charge, 3 damage if pushed).","(1) Germinate | Create area of thick vegetation counting as severe terrain anywhere within 8 yards. 3 yards diameter. Lasts indefinitely."],"notes":"Tree spirits of Malifaux. Typically non-violent. Roused to anger by destruction of forests by lumberjacks. Bound into service with eldritch magic. Thick bark resists damage. Force roots to entangle."}}
{"_id":"stitched-together","name":"Stitched Together","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Construct, Doll, Nightmare","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":-2,"speed":-1,"resilience":2,"charm":-4,"cunning":2,"intellect":0,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"4","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"2 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"convince":{"value":2},"enchanting":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":2},"gambling":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Eternal Nightmare","description":"If would reduce to 0 Wounds, may discard card to heal 3 Wounds and gain Reactivate."},{"name":"Rotten Contents","description":"When suffering Critical Effect or killed, Living within p2 must pass TN 12 Carouse or gain Poison +2."},{"name":"Rush +2","description":"Charge Aspect increased by +2."}],"actions":["(1) Hook Hands (Melee) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage.","(1) Gamble Your Life (Gambling) | AV: 5m (11m) | TN: 10M | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 3/4/6 damage. If resist, character suffers 3/4/6. No Cheat, ignore +/-. Once per turn.","(1) The Mist (Enchanting) | AV: 5C (11C) | TN: 10C | Until start of next turn, area within a4 is Ht 3 soft cover."],"notes":"Bad dreams stepped into reality. Burlap puppets filled with rotten meat and offal. Torment living. Force victims to wager body parts. Create new Stitched Together from bodies."}}
{"_id":"marionette","name":"Marionette","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct, Doll","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":0,"charm":1,"cunning":2,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (10)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"1","initiative":"2 (7)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"evade":{"value":3},"pugilism":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Adorable Doll","description":"Indistinguishable from normal doll when not moving."},{"name":"Flick of the Wrist","description":"May use Grace instead of Might for Melee/Pugilism attacks."},{"name":"Trailing Strings","description":"If no character holding strings, Enforcer/Henchman/Master/Fated within 2 yards may seize as (0) Action. Cannot use two-handed/cast Spells. One Marionette per character."},{"name":"Tangled Up","description":"While enemy holds strings, character is Slow."},{"name":"Puppet Show","description":"Friendly holding strings gains + to attacks, use their Skill ranks instead. Spend 1 AP to force (1) Action of choice."}],"actions":["(1) Wooden Fists (Pugilism) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage. May add Grace of friendly holding strings to duel total. Tome Made to Follow: After resolving, if not character's turn, take action again.","(0) Dragging Along | Character moves up to 2 yards. If character holding strings, it pushed 2 yards directly toward."],"notes":"Wooden puppets with trapped souls of children. Created by Collodi. Act mostly own volition but bound by strings. Newly created tend toward depression. Time shatters minds into cruel predators."}}
{"_id":"wicked-doll","name":"Wicked Doll","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct, Doll","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":0,"charm":2,"cunning":1,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"6 (11)","willpower":"5 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"1","initiative":"3 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"bewitch":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":4},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":1},"scrutiny":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":3},"stitching":{"value":2},"thrownWeapons":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Adorable Doll","description":"Indistinguishable from normal doll when not moving."},{"name":"Flick of the Wrist","description":"May use Grace instead of Might for Melee/Pugilism attacks."},{"name":"Malice Aura","description":"When Living suffers damage from non-Poison source within a1, also gains Poison +1."}],"actions":["(1) Knife (Melee) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage. Crow Hamstring: +1 damage, falls Prone, gains Useless Limb (Legs) until healed.","(1) Thrown Needles (Thrown Weapons) | AV: 5M (10M) | Rg: z9 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/1/1B damage. No randomize in engagement. Mask Attached Threads: After succeeding, push character into contact with target.","(1) All Sewed Up | Target other Doll within 1 yard heals 1 damage and gains New Threads Condition 24 hours (gains + to attacks)."],"notes":"Voodoo dolls filled with hatred and spite. Sewn from burlap, cloth, or human flesh anointed with target blood. Creep into homes to stab victims in sleep. Use bundles of needles as weapons."}}
{"_id":"rougarou","name":"Rougarou","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Undead, Beast, Fae","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":3,"charm":-4,"cunning":3,"intellect":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (11)","willpower":"5 (12)","walk":"5","charge":"7","height":"3","initiative":"5 (12)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":9},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":2},"athletics":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":3},"deceive":{"value":2},"intimidate":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"pugilism":{"value":2},"scrutiny":{"value":1},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":3},"track":{"value":4},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Diving Charge","description":"May declare Charge while engaged. Ignores intervening characters, terrain, opponents cannot Disengage."},{"name":"Hard to Wound +1","description":"Damage flips against this character suffer -."},{"name":"Rush +1","description":"Charge Aspect increased by +1."}],"actions":["(1) Wulfen Claws (Pugilism) | AV: 6 (13) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/4/6 damage. Ram Crushing Strike: Damage flip gains + per Ram.","(2) The Mauling (Pugilism) | AV: 6 (13) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage and Critical Hit of appropriate severity. Crow Eat Anything: After damaging Living/Undead, heal 1 damage.","(0) Howl to the Blood Moon (Intimidate) | Discard card. Every Living within p10 makes TN 13 Centering Challenge. Failed gain Prey Condition until next turn (no Charge, Walk only in melee)."],"notes":"Massive undead wolves. Servants of Titania, Autumn Queen of Fae. Keenly intelligent and cunning assassins. Roam Knotwoods hunting Neverborn and human. Dangerous regardless of moon phase."}}
{"_id":"bayou-gremlin","name":"Bayou Gremlin","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living, Gremlin","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":2,"speed":1,"resilience":0,"charm":-2,"cunning":1,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":1},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"3 (8)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"1","initiative":"2 (7)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"barter":{"value":1},"carouse":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":2},"gambling":{"value":1},"homesteading":{"value":1},"husbandry":{"value":1},"longArms":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":2},"music":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":1},"pickPocket":{"value":1},"track":{"value":1},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Drunk and Reckless","description":"If Intoxicated, may suffer 2 damage at start of turn to gain additional General AP."},{"name":"From the Hip","description":"Uses Grace instead of Intellect for Long Arm attacks."},{"name":"Squeal (Mask)","description":"After damaged by enemy Close Combat, push 4 yards directly away."}],"actions":["(1) Banjo Bash (Melee) | AV: 1 (6) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/2/4 damage. If Critical Effect, breaks and ceases function.","(1) Boomstick (Long Arms) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3B damage. Must declare Trigger. Capacity 1, Reload 1. Ram Dumb Luck: Double damage, suffer half. Crow Whoops Ricochet: Closest char within range suffers 1 damage. Tome What If: Add +B to Moderate/Severe. Mask I Got Him: After succeeding, push 3 yards toward target."],"notes":"Most intelligent creatures of Bayou. Raised through mimicry. Learn from humans: clothing, firearms, walls, pig domestication, moonshine brewing. Population booming. Serious threat to Guild dominance."}}
{"_id":"bayou-boss","name":"Bayou Boss","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":8},"types":"Living, Gremlin","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":3,"charm":-2,"cunning":3,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (13)","willpower":"6 (14)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"5 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":9},"skills":{"barter":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":4},"centering":{"value":4},"deceive":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"gambling":{"value":2},"leadership":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":3},"music":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":3},"shotgun":{"value":3},"thrownWeapons":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":3},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Encouragement","description":"Friendly within 6 yards may suffer 1 damage when performing Action to gain + to flip."},{"name":"Gremlin Boss","description":"Accompanied by friendly Bayou Gremlins equal to Rank Value."},{"name":"Delegate (Tome)","description":"After attack succeeds, instead affects friendly character within 3 yards."}],"actions":["(1) Shotgun | AV varies | Rg: z12 | Various effects with Shotgun triggers","(1) Melee | AV varies | Rg: y1-2 | Various close combat effects"],"notes":"Prolific successful Gremlins who never stop growing. Largest of their kind. Bully smaller Gremlins into subservience. Gremlin society revolves around Bayou Bosses. Determine village politics and feuds."}}
{"_id":"slop-hauler","name":"Slop Hauler","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Gremlin","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-3,"cunning":1,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"1","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":5},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":2},"homesteading":{"value":2},"husbandry":{"value":2},"melee":{"value":2},"music":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":2},"thrownWeapons":{"value":3},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"One Eye on the Pigs","description":"At start of turn, if Pig within 3 yards, generate additional AP only for Movement General Action."},{"name":"Squeal (Mask)","description":"After damaged by enemy Close Combat attack, push 4 yards directly away."}],"actions":["(1) Slop Bucket (Melee) | AV: 2C (8C) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/2 damage. Crow Full of Slop: After succeeding, take Tossed Slop Action even if engaged.","(1) Tossed Slop (Thrown Weapon) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: z9 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3B damage. Gains Covered in Slop Condition until washed off (- to Social duels, cannot declare Triggers, Pigs gain + to attacks). Mask Come and Get It: Every Pig within p5 pushes 5 yards toward and makes y attack. Capacity 1, Reload 1."],"notes":"Coveted position among Gremlins due to food perks. Get first pick of pig food. Quick on feet to avoid becoming main course. Throw disgusting slop at enemies."}}
{"_id":"moon-shinobi","name":"Moon Shinobi","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living, Gremlin","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":1,"cunning":1,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"6 (13)","willpower":"4 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"1","initiative":"5 (12)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":8},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":2},"bewitch":{"value":3},"carouse":{"value":5},"culinary":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":4},"gambling":{"value":1},"martialArts":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"pickPocket":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":3},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Drunk and Reckless","description":"If Intoxicated, may suffer 2 damage at start of turn to gain additional General AP."},{"name":"Drunken Gremlin Kung Fu","description":"Always Intoxicated (suffers - to Willpower duels). When attacked by Close/Ranged, attacker counts + as - and - as +."},{"name":"Numb the Pain","description":"While Intoxicated, ignores effects of Weak and Moderate Critical Effects."}],"actions":["(1) Tiny Green Fists of Fury (Martial Arts) | AV: 5 (12) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage. Severe inflicts Weak Critical Effect. Ram Critical Strike: +1 damage per Ram. Mask Drunken Roundhouse: After succeeding, take action again vs different character.","(1) Have a Drink (Bewitch) | AV: 4 (11) | Rg: 1 | Resist: Wp | Living target gains Intoxicated Condition 10 min or Poison +1 if already. Crow Bit Woozy: After succeeding, Slow. Ram Liver Damage: After succeeding, suffers 1/3/4 damage."],"notes":"Serve enigmatic Brewmaster. Renounce family ties, swear loyalty. Receive all alcohol. Survive initiation through Drunken Gremlin Kung Fu training. Kept drunk throughout training."}}
{"_id":"piglet","name":"Piglet","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Peon","value":4},"types":"Living, Beast, Pig","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":0,"speed":3,"resilience":0,"charm":-3,"cunning":-3,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":1},"derived":{"defense":"5 (9)","willpower":"3 (7)","walk":"6","charge":"7","height":"1","initiative":"4 (8)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"skills":{"notice":{"value":1},"pugilism":{"value":1},"track":{"value":1},"wilderness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Pigcharge","description":"May perform (2) Charge Action as (1) Action."},{"name":"Puny","description":"Has -1 Wounds and cannot make Disengaging Strikes."},{"name":"Set Er Off","description":"At start of turn during Dramatic Time, if not engaged or within 2 yards of friendly without this Ability, must declare Charge vs closest legal non-Pig target."}],"actions":["(1) Ram (Pugilism) | AV: 3 (7) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/3 damage. As part of Charge, +1 per yard moved before attack. Must declare Trigger. Ram Stampede: After damaging, must declare Charge vs closest non-Pig not engaged. Crow Eat Anything: After damaging Living/Undead, heal 1. Tome Grab On: Target gains Clamped On +1 (-1 Walk, -2 Charge, +1 damage). Mask Bowled Over: Target TN 10 Acrobatics or Prone."],"notes":"Baby pigs that grow into adults. Easier to train than adults. Raised as pets by Gremlins. Useful self-defense but can't be left unsupervised. Follow mothers in wild."}}
{"_id":"bayou-pig","name":"Bayou Pig","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Beast, Pig","aspects":{"might":3,"grace":0,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":-4,"cunning":-2,"intellect":-1,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":2},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Pigcharge","description":"May perform (2) Charge Action as (1) Action."},{"name":"Set Er Off","description":"At start of turn during Dramatic Time, if not engaged or within 2 yards of friendly without this Ability, must declare Charge vs closest legal non-Pig target."},{"name":"Eat Like A Pig","description":"After killing Living/Undead with Close Combat attack, may immediately end turn to heal 3 damage."}],"actions":["(1) Tusks (Pugilism) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Must declare Trigger. Ram Stampede: After damaging, must declare Charge vs closest non-Pig not engaged. Crow Eat Anything: After damaging Living/Undead, heal 1. Tome Tossed Up: After succeeding, place target 2 yards away, becomes Prone. Mask Trampling: Target TN 12 Acrobatics or suffers 1 damage, Prone."],"notes":"Voracious killing machines. Thick leather skin and massive tusks. Knock adult humans down. Wild pigs kept Gremlin population culled. Now Gremlins hunt and domesticate them."}}
{"_id":"bayou-gator","name":"Bayou Gator","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Swampfiend, Beast","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":-3,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":-4,"cunning":1,"intellect":-3,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":1},"intimidate":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Melee Expert","description":"Generates additional AP on turn, may only use for Close Combat attack."},{"name":"Aquatic","description":"Speed not reduced while swimming. Can take Charge Action underwater."},{"name":"Ruthless","description":"Automatically succeeds at any Willpower duel it attempts during turn."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Fearsome Jaws (Pugilism) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage. Ram Death Roll: When damaging, Attack gains + to damage flip, target Prone. Crow Swallow Whole: After damaging target with lower Height, target must discard card or be killed and eaten.","(0) Creep | Character/controller may discard card to move distance equal to Walk."],"notes":"Most efficient ambush predators of swamps. Wait in/near water looking like logs. Drag prey to water to drown. Perform death roll to dismember. Hungry ones charge staggering distances."}}
{"_id":"bayou-chicken","name":"Bayou Chicken","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living, Beast","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":1,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":0,"cunning":-1,"intellect":-2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Rampage","description":"At start of turn, if 0 or fewer Wounds, must declare Charge vs closest legal target not engaged. If engaged, still declare Charge but only single Attack. Gains + to attack and damage."},{"name":"Roostercharge","description":"May perform (2) Charge Action as (1) Action."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Beak (Pugilism) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/5 damage. Must declare Trigger. Ram BU-GAWK: After damaging, must declare Charge vs closest target. If engaged, suffers 1 damage. Crow Foot Spurs: If male, target Dazed until end of next turn. Already Dazed gets +1 damage.","(0) Delicious Egg | If female, discard card to lay egg adjacent. Within a5 of egg, Chickens gain + to Defense. Egg fresh 2 weeks."],"notes":"Six-foot-tall birds brought 100 years ago. Malifaux magic seeped into generations. Prolific spread until Gremlins noticed delicious eggs. High-strung and paranoid from constant nest raids."}}
{"_id":"union-thug","name":"Union Thug","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":3,"grace":0,"speed":0,"resilience":2,"charm":-1,"cunning":-1,"intellect":0,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"4 (9)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"0 (5)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":2},"intimidate":{"value":3},"pugilism":{"value":2},"scrutiny":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Eat Lightning","description":"When suffers damage, gains Adrenaline +1 until end of Dramatic Time (heals 1 damage at round end, lower by 1)."},{"name":"Hand-Picked Men","description":"Gains + to attack and damage flips within 6 yards of friendly Enforcer/Henchman/Master."}],"actions":["(1) Brass Knuckles (Pugilism) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Weapon gains + to damage flip. Ram Broken Nose: After damaging, target Dazed until healed. Crow Aim Low: After damaging, target Slow.","(1) You Lookin At Me? (Intimidate) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: 8 | Resist: Wp | If target can be Charged, immediately declares Charge vs this character even if engaged. Successful attacks suffer -- to damage flip. If successful Charge, becomes Paralyzed."],"notes":"Strong unsubtle enforcement arm of Union. Former convicts and rough laborers. Enforce Union will through intimidation and violence. Rewarded with good pay and legal protection."}}
{"_id":"steamborg-executioner","name":"Steamborg Executioner","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Henchman","value":9},"types":"Construct, Living","aspects":{"might":4,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":4,"charm":-3,"intellect":0,"cunning":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"3 (12)","willpower":"5 (14)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"3","initiative":"4 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":11},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":2},"athletics":{"value":4},"carouse":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":5},"notice":{"value":2},"pugilism":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":5}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +2","description":"Reduce all damage by +2 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Nimble","description":"Generates additional AP on turn, only for Movement General Action."},{"name":"Terrifying (Living) (12)","description":"Enemy Living must pass TN 12 Horror Duel when ending turn in engagement range or targeting."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Reinforced Executioner Claw (Pugilism) | AV: 7C (16C) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 4/5/6 damage. Ram+Crow Decapitate: After damaging, target must discard two Twist or be killed. Mask+Crow Rip in Half: After killing, all enemies within p6 make TN 12 Horror Duel.","(0) Vent Steam | Until start of next turn, area within a4 is Ht 5 soft cover.","(2) Flurry | Discard Twist Card to take three 1 AP attacks with Close Combat weapon vs single target."],"notes":"Amalgamations of flesh and steel. Injured miners saved and transformed by Viktor Ramos. Nearly fanatical loyalty to Union. Fearsome combatants shrug off punishment."}}
{"_id":"gunsmith","name":"Gunsmith","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":2,"charm":1,"intellect":1,"cunning":2,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"5 (11)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"barter":{"value":2},"carouse":{"value":1},"convince":{"value":3},"enchanting":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":3},"intimidate":{"value":4},"notice":{"value":2},"pistol":{"value":4},"scrutiny":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Return Fire (Mask)","description":"After succeeding at Defense/Willpower duel, attacker suffers damage from readied Pistol weapon. Damage flip receives -."},{"name":"Always Ready","description":"May take Ready Weapon Action immediately after flipping Initiative."},{"name":"Gunfighter","description":"May use Pistols as if Range y2."},{"name":"Hard to Kill","description":"May choose to ignore one Critical Effect per Dramatic Time."}],"actions":["(1) Custom Pistol (Pistol) | AV: 6 (12) | Rg: z12 or y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. If Rapid Fire, +2 to final duel total. Capacity 8, Reload 0. Tome Piercing: Ignores Armor/Hard to Wound. Mask Experimental: 2/4/6 damage. Ram Explosive: +B to Moderate/Severe. Crow Cavity: + to damage.","(2) Rapid Fire | Discard Twist Card to take three 1 AP attacks with Ranged weapon vs single target."],"notes":"Elite troubleshooters of M&SU. Carry heavily modified pistols with specialized ammunition. Reputation alone often resolves conflicts. Devastating when pressed."}}
{"_id":"showgirl","name":"Showgirl","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Living, Belle","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":-2,"charm":3,"cunning":2,"intellect":1,"tenacity":1},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"3 (8)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"4 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"art":{"value":2},"bewitch":{"value":3},"convince":{"value":2},"deceive":{"value":3},"literacy":{"value":1},"melee":{"value":2},"music":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":2},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"stitching":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Distracting Performance","description":"When performing, allies within 10 yards gain + to Deceive, Pick Pocket, Stealth Challenges."},{"name":"Flick of the Wrist","description":"May use Grace instead of Might for Melee/Pugilism attacks."},{"name":"Manipulative (10)","description":"When enemy targets this character, they must pass TN 10 Willpower. On failure, may change target to legal choice."}],"actions":["(1) Poisoned Hairpin (Melee) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/1/2 damage, gains Poison +1.","(1) Lure (Bewitch) | AV: 6 (11) | Rg: 18 | Resist: Wp | Living target moves toward this character. Mask Fatal Distraction: Friendly within 5 yards may make 1 AP attack.","(1) Expensive Gift (Bewitch) | AV: 6 (11) | Rg: 2 | Resist: Wp | Living target gives this character non-weapon item from hand."],"notes":"Beautiful, charming performers at Star Theater. Secretly trained Arcanist agents. Assist with Soulstone smuggling. Wield subtle stage and shadow magic."}}
{"_id":"steamfitter","name":"Steamfitter","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":1,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-1,"cunning":2,"intellect":2,"tenacity":-1},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"3 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"artefacting":{"value":3},"bureaucracy":{"value":1},"centering":{"value":2},"enchanting":{"value":3},"engineering":{"value":2},"intimidate":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":1},"scrutiny":{"value":1},"sorcery":{"value":4},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Killswitch","description":"After subordinate Construct killed, may discard card to detonate it, 2 damage within p2."},{"name":"My Creation","description":"Accompanied by and may control single non-Swarm Construct of Minion Rank or lower."}],"actions":["(1) Freezing Touch (Sorcery/Intellect) | AV: 6t (12t) | TN: 12t | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage, becomes Slow.","(1) Lightning Bolt (Sorcery/Intellect) | AV: 6t (12t) | TN: 12t | Rg: z10 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage, ignoring Armor. No randomize on engaged.","(1) Enchant Weapon (Enchanting/Cunning) | AV: 5R (11R) | TN: 11R | Rg: 1 | Resist: Df | Target weapon gains Electric or Ice effect 1 minute."],"notes":"Magical backbone of Arcanist movement. Officially maintain Union constructs. Skilled spellcasters with hidden vaults of Arcanist knowledge."}}
{"_id":"oxfordian-mage","name":"Oxfordian Mage","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living, Academic","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":1,"speed":0,"resilience":2,"charm":1,"cunning":2,"intellect":3,"tenacity":3},"derived":{"defense":"4 (11)","willpower":"5 (12)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"3 (10)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"enchanting":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":2},"history":{"value":3},"literacy":{"value":4},"mathematics":{"value":2},"necromancy":{"value":2},"notice":{"value":3},"prestidigitation":{"value":3},"scrutiny":{"value":2},"sorcery":{"value":4},"stealth":{"value":1},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Counterspell","description":"When targeted by enemy Magical Action, enemy loses any suit from Magical Skill."},{"name":"Magical Shielding","description":"Friendly within a6 reduce damage by 1 (minimum 0)."},{"name":"Ritualistic Caster","description":"May declare any Triggers including same Trigger multiple times. Each suit pays for single Trigger."},{"name":"The Ritual Has Begun","description":"Peon/Minion within a6 may assist ritual (2 AP for +rtcm to Magical). Academic treat as (1)."}],"actions":["(2) Elemental Bolt (Sorcery/Intellect) | AV: 7t (14t) | TN: 14t | Rg: z10 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage. Tome Fire: Burning +1. Tome Ice: Slow. Tome Electric: Ignores Armor. Tome Wind: Push 2 yards.","(2) Teleport (Prestidigitation/Intellect) | AV: 6m (13m) | TN: 10m | Rg: 10 | Resist: Wp | Target instantly teleported to safe location in range."],"notes":"Graduates of Oxford University of Metaphysical Studies. Smuggled by Arcanists. Ritualistic casting chains Triggers. Grow exponentially dangerous together."}}
{"_id":"soulstone-driller","name":"Soulstone Driller","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct","aspects":{"might":3,"grace":-1,"speed":-1,"resilience":2,"charm":-5,"cunning":-5,"intellect":-5,"tenacity":-5},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"3 (8)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"-1 (4)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"centering":{"value":1},"evade":{"value":3},"pneumatic":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by +1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Burrowing Charge","description":"When Charge, may make single 2 AP Close Combat attack instead of two 1 AP."},{"name":"Rock Drill","description":"May move through solid stone without speed reduction. May leave tunnel behind."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(2) Pneumatic Drill (Pneumatic) | AV: 6 (11) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 4/5/7 damage, ignoring Armor. Mask Excavation: Creates 2 yard deep hole. TN 10 Evade or fall Prone."],"notes":"Worm-like mining constructs by Viktor Ramos. Sense and burrow toward Soulstone deposits. Tunnel underground, burst beneath enemies, drill through anything."}}
{"_id":"rock-hopper","name":"Rock Hopper","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct","aspects":{"might":2,"grace":-1,"speed":-1,"resilience":1,"charm":-5,"cunning":-5,"intellect":-5,"tenacity":-5},"derived":{"defense":"2 (7)","willpower":"2 (7)","walk":"4","charge":"4","height":"2","initiative":"-1 (4)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"heavyMelee":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":1},"pneumatic":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":2}},"abilities":[{"name":"Grinding Halt (Tome)","description":"Immediately gains Armor +2 for duration of Action."},{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by +1 (minimum 1)."}],"actions":["(1) Mining Pick (Heavy Melee) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/4 damage.","(2) Pneumatic Drill (Pneumatic) | AV: 5 (10) | Rg: y2 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 4/5/7 damage, ignoring Armor."],"notes":"M&SU most common mining construct. Reliable if clumsy. Bore through solid stone. Pressed into combat service."}}
{"_id":"steam-arachnid","name":"Steam Arachnid","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":5},"types":"Construct","aspects":{"might":0,"grace":1,"speed":1,"resilience":0,"charm":-5,"cunning":-5,"intellect":-5,"tenacity":-5},"derived":{"defense":"4 (9)","willpower":"2 (7)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"1","initiative":"1 (6)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":4},"skills":{"evade":{"value":3},"pneumatic":{"value":4},"stealth":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Armor +1","description":"Reduce all damage by +1 (minimum 1)."},{"name":"Evasive","description":"Immune to damage from pulse (p) effects."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Steel Claws (Pneumatic) | AV: 4 (9) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/2/4 damage. Tome Overheat: Destroy this character, everyone within p2 suffers 2 damage.","(0) Swarm Together | This character and at least one other friendly within a3 become Steam Arachnid Swarm with Rank Value Condition."],"notes":"Small spider-like spy constructs for Arcanists. Weak individually. Programmed to merge into deadly swarms."}}
{"_id":"arcanist-smuggler","name":"Arcanist Smuggler","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":2,"resilience":0,"charm":0,"cunning":3,"intellect":2,"tenacity":-1},"derived":{"defense":"5 (11)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"5 (11)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":5},"skills":{"athletics":{"value":2},"barter":{"value":3},"centering":{"value":2},"convince":{"value":1},"deceive":{"value":3},"evade":{"value":3},"forgery":{"value":2},"lockpicking":{"value":1},"melee":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"pistol":{"value":2},"scrutiny":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Don't Mind Me (12)","description":"If no offensive actions last turn or first round not acted, enemies TN 12 Scrutiny or choose different target."},{"name":"Slink Away","description":"Gain + to Defense against disengaging strikes. If friendly engaged, enemy cannot make disengaging strikes vs this."},{"name":"Unimpeded","description":"Ignores terrain penalties when taking Movement Actions."}],"actions":["(1) Hunting Knife (Melee) | AV: 4 (10) | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage.","(1) Quick-Draw Hold-Out Pistol (Pistol) | AV: 4 (10) | Rg: z6 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/3/3 damage. Ready as (0). Gains + to attack, target cannot declare Defensive Triggers. Capacity 4, Reload 2."],"notes":"Paranoid operatives moving stolen Soulstones through checkpoints. Use hidden compartments, bribery, magic. Caught = death. Exceptionally cautious."}}
{"_id":"december-cultist","name":"December Cultist","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Minion","value":6},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":1,"grace":2,"speed":1,"resilience":1,"charm":-2,"cunning":2,"intellect":2,"tenacity":1},"derived":{"defense":"4 (10)","willpower":"4 (10)","walk":"5","charge":"5","height":"2","initiative":"3 (9)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":7},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":1},"archery":{"value":3},"athletics":{"value":1},"centering":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":2},"homesteading":{"value":1},"notice":{"value":2},"sorcery":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":2},"toughness":{"value":2},"track":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":3}},"abilities":[{"name":"Frozen Heart","description":"Immune to Horror Duels and Paralyzed Condition."},{"name":"From the Shadows","description":"On Initiative, if no enemy aware unfriendly, may take additional turn before Initiative order for each instance."}],"actions":["(1) Frozen Touch (Sorcery/Intellect) | AV: 5t (11t) | TN: 10t | Rg: y1 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage, Slow.","(1) Harpoon Gun (Archery) | AV: 5 (11) | Rg: z12 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 2/4/6 damage, Slow. Ram Pull: Push toward you yards = Might. Capacity 1, Reload 2.","(2) Grim Feast | Devour Living/Undead Minion+ corpse within 1 yard. Gain Well Fed +1 (1 hour) giving +1 Physical (max 4)."],"notes":"Fanatical Tyrant December servants. Desperate lowlanders. Embrace cannibalism. Frost magic and harpoons. Allied with Arcanists via Rasputina."}}
{"_id":"thunder-archer","name":"Thunder Archer","type":"fatemaster","system":{"rank":{"title":"Enforcer","value":7},"types":"Living","aspects":{"might":-1,"grace":3,"speed":2,"resilience":1,"charm":-2,"cunning":0,"intellect":2,"tenacity":2},"derived":{"defense":"4 (11)","willpower":"5 (12)","walk":"5","charge":"6","height":"2","initiative":"6 (13)"},"wounds":{"value":0,"max":6},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"value":4},"archery":{"value":5},"athletics":{"value":3},"carouse":{"value":1},"deceive":{"value":2},"evade":{"value":4},"history":{"value":2},"intimidate":{"value":3},"martial":{"value":3},"notice":{"value":3},"stealth":{"value":3},"toughness":{"value":2},"wilderness":{"value":1}},"abilities":[{"name":"Arrows of the Silent Eye","description":"Each Arrow used gets special capability vs different targets (Piercing vs Armor, Burning, Weak CF, Paralyze, Fear/Slow)."},{"name":"Flurry of Arrows","description":"May discard card to make three 1 AP Archery attacks vs different targets."},{"name":"Wall of Arrows","description":"When another character within a6 is targeted by attack, may discard card to use Archery vs attacker instead. TN 10."}],"actions":["(1) Arrows of the Silent Eye (Archery) | AV: 5 (12) | Rg: z14 | Resist: Df | Target suffers 1/3/4 damage. Triggers determine effect vs armor/burning/weak/paralyze/fear. Capacity 8."],"notes":"Elite archers serving Ten Thunders. Tradition descending from Archers of Silent Eye. Masters of bow and martial arts. Wear eye-engraved helmets."}}
